buffalo3d.vos

Class Number3d

  • java.lang.Object
    • buffalo3d.vos.Number3d

  • public class Number3d
extends Object
    Simple VO holding x,y, and z values. Plus helper math functions. Care should be taken to avoid creating Number3d instances unnecessarily. Its use is not required for the construction of vertices.
